        assertthat, magrittr, Rcpp (>= 0.12.3), zoo, lazyeval, purrr
LinkingTo: Rcpp
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
Suggests: testthat, taxstats, rmarkdown, dtplyr, ggplot2, scales,
        broom, knitr, survey, viridis, ggrepel
